39) DISPLAY NAME, SAL, HRA, PF, DA, TOTAL SAL FOR EACH EMPLOYEE. 
    THE OUTPUT SHOULD BE IN THE ORDER OF TOTAL SAL, HRA 15% OF SAL, 
    DA 10% OF SAL, PF 5% OF SAL TOTAL SALARY WILL BE (SAL+HRA+DA)-PF

select Employee_Name, 
Salary, 
Salary*15/100 as 'HRA', 
Salary*10/100 as 'DA', 
Salary*5/100 as 'PF', 
(Salary + 'HRA' + 'DA') - 'PF' as 'Total Salary' from Employee;
